reviewText: Same old, same old....if I had known it was done by Tim Lahaye and Thomas Ice I would have passed on it.  There are other viable views regarding the end times.  Please investigate the Preterist view on the subject.  The end times will never be more clear to you.
This is more of a sermon, which was disappointing as we were looking for a documentary. I would suggest reading the books of Ezekiel; Isaiah; Daniel, Matthew 24,25; and Revelation.
On time. Product as advertised. Excellent experience!
